# PoseFinder 📸

PoseFinder is a Python project that helps users discover photography pose ideas more efficiently.

## Features
- Accepts outfit, location, gender, and vibe as input
- Generates personalized Pinterest search suggestions
- Displays multiple pose-related search keywords
- Opens Pinterest search results automatically

## Technologies Used
- Python
- webbrowser
- urllib

